   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Clean Water for 6500 Villagers in Cameroon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In cameroon, people live in poverty everyday due to lack of clean water sources. water sources that are available are polluted and are located very far away. Chances are even high that future generations could face the same water crises if action is not taken.With the help of individual donors like you, we have dramatically changed the lives of more than 8,500 rural villagers deep in the Cameroonian bush where people walk up to 7km to fetch water.</narrative>
  </description>
